= SDL_MapRGBA =
Use this function to map an RGBA quadruple to a pixel value for a given pixel format.


== Syntax ==
```c++
Uint32 SDL_MapRGBA(const SDL_PixelFormat* format,
                   Uint8                  r, 
                   Uint8                  g, 
                   Uint8                  b,
                   Uint8                  a)
